FEATURES Available in 3 Colours and 3 Sizes Scoops good quantities of litter at one time Strong, Lightweight & Durable High Quality Plastic Easy to Use Long Handled Cat Litter Scoop available Compatible with most Cat Litter Trays MATERIAL : - PLASTIC SIZE AVAILABLE Small : 23cm x 10cm x 3cm Medium : 34cm x 12cm x 5cm Large : 40cm x 14cm x 6cm Directions Firstly, choose the right size of Cat Litter Scoop for your Cat Litter Tray or Litter Box. Then, hold the scoop at the bottom of the litter box and dig into the litter to fill it. You can move left to right or work methodically through the box. As you scoop, shake the scoop gently from side to side to let litter fall through the slots and back into the box. The clumps of urine and feces will remain in the scoop.
